{"tid":218792,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有冇taco/burrito好食？","createTime":"2017-04-26T17:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T16:01:12.000Z","uid":266,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c18bb431b50c489a05785fb0f716cd2d355dc2d8","tid":218792,"uid":266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:33:18.000Z","msg":"如題 唔知點解忽然想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日見香港好多少日本野 韓國野<br />\n但taco呢啲好似好少見到 淨係見過旺角登打士街有間<br />\nBurrito:<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.tacobueno.com/assets/food/burritos/Burrito_BOB_990x725.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.tacobueno.com%2Fassets%2Ffood%2Fburritos%2FBurrito_BOB_990x725.jpg&h=bd7b5905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTaco:<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.tacobueno.com/assets/food/tacos/Taco_Soft_Beef_990x725.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.tacobueno.com%2Fassets%2Ffood%2Ftacos%2FTaco_Soft_Beef_990x725.jpg&h=551066b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc4ce357296532718c00fdb0d3a007e2bfec2adf","tid":218792,"uid":83711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:39:30.000Z","msg":"屌，墨仔野真係好好味<br />\n可惜香港無乜人識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eda706a75236c95d8870266673d5aea20d1c31ec","tid":218792,"uid":4863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:52:31.000Z","msg":"Tst tequila's jack 唔錯"},{"pid":"e9b81cdc9d8c56615cf2cb89c844b50d2c68df6d","tid":218792,"uid":51981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T18:11:02.000Z","msg":"屌岩岩先講完想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7291df5007e214c7d054c8762d7b057bf7bfaaaf","tid":218792,"uid":58639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T18:16:16.000Z","msg":"中環brickhouse不錯"},{"pid":"ac0601b4e479e15e00c00311c0f47a39197187e8","tid":218792,"uid":30309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s