/>\n買個SHELL 番黎<br />\nsour cream, salsa, cheese , ground beef 炒炒,生菜仲有其他配料撈埋一舊好好味已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ce337db7a71d606e239b7938af3063e7ca40aa","tid":218792,"uid":93547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:53:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梗係食 fajitas <br />\n仲有FISH TACO <br />\n普通TACO其實自然整都得<br />\n買個SHELL 番黎<br />\nsour cream, salsa, cheese , ground beef 炒炒,生菜仲有其他配料撈埋一舊好好味已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e896a8c9706b8ac54a774d344a90ec8296ba6338","tid":218792,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:56:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>尖沙咀tequlia jack</blockquote><br />\n呢間係咪酒吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n見openrice啲食評講到happyhour果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入去淨係食野 飲1-2杯酒會唔會好怪</blockquote><br />\n唔會，我成日係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9193fb96e34388a9f6188c2ec07c46ba68df463f","tid":218792,"uid":266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:28:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梗係食 fajitas <br />\n仲有FISH TACO <br />\n普通TACO其實自然整都得<br />\n買個SHELL 番黎<br />\nsour cream, salsa, cheese , ground beef 炒炒,生菜仲有其他配料撈埋一舊好好味已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲shell係邊度有得買？<br />\nCityS____會唔會有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7260e241c8ada5b31ec377d3212247d556d67e","tid":218792,"uid":45678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:42:03.000Z","msg":"大坑Andy's garage唔錯"},{"pid":"34295974748d192a770489d3be399cc7ec91ed65","tid":218792,"uid":88125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:20:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>梗係食 fajitas <br />\n仲有FISH TACO <br />\n普通TACO其實自然整都得<br />\n買個SHELL 番黎<br />\nsour cream, salsa, cheese , ground beef 炒炒,生菜仲有其他配料撈埋一舊好好味已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲shell係邊度有得買？<br />\nCityS____會唔會有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n馬莎有taco set(hard shell), 分開 soft flour tortilla 同 taco seasoning 都有得賣(不過唔係間間有)<br />\n一田都有 soft flour tortilla(好似冇馬莎咁厚)"},{"pid":"8e6775fc528354cf2012388db6abb87232e9790c","tid":218792,"uid":67862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:26:48.000Z","msg":"西環 Tequila on Davis"},{"pid":"5afe023b998c87a950a69f69c147027fa0439b7c","tid":218792,"uid":52323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:43:09.000Z","msg":"香港吊高晒嚟賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023ae9fccb4845bb1a2519570d7c2538f5925d05","tid":218792,"uid":69794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:45:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港吊高晒嚟賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港幾時先有taco bell做爛市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc659a9e873ffeb66aee37486fce59777d28fa25","tid":218792,"uid":28590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:51:49.000Z","msg":"鍾意 burrito 多過 taco"},{"pid":"e1fe7ee68c1e52af5dd279a776dd2af908a54370","tid":218792,"uid":9146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:54:43.000Z","msg":"trortilla, taaco, burrito 三者有咩唔同?"},{"pid":"36388ffced1a2a060dae23b3c642f40b1325aa63","tid":218792,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:58:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人試過cali mex</blockquote><br />\n正，成日食，周圍都有，又飽！burrito bowl都ok<br />\n咁當然無美國/墨西哥咁正啦....好想再去墨西哥食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTst tequila jack去過，無burrito的，taco tuesday就10蚊一個taco，但其實就好hea料唔算多，真係當小食送下酒就算，想食幾個填飽個肚就不如去calimex食個好味既taco/burrito<br />\n反而nacho就必食，buffalo wings都ok(其實nacho又好難唔好食既....)<br />\n<br />\nTaco bell之外我都想要in &amp; out呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1131d4c70f34a075659743299e065dea5aee836","tid":218792,"uid":58639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:12:23.000Z","msg":"今日去左諾士佛臺間Port<br />\n個nacho幾好食 但taco就好麻麻<br />\n<br />\n想問香港邊到有好食嘅quesadilla[?"},{"pid":"f2feac55b5ec13235f289a52c73ebd3245e15253","tid":218792,"uid":48211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:15:45.000Z","msg":"Fish taco真係不得了<br />\n<br />\n利申:唔鐘意食佢啲豆"},{"pid":"fadacbdefd664ec23e09157d32a0449840afb994","tid":218792,"uid":96708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:16:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>trortilla, taaco, burrito 三者有咩唔同?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://images.wisegeek.com/flour-tortilla.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.wisegeek.com%2Fflour-tortilla.jpg&h=87d51f41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTortilla就係一塊塊圓形粟米餅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rubios.com/sites/default/files/styles/menu_item_cropped/public/menu/Grilled-Mahi-Burrito_0.jpg?itok=3KPkkW_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rubios.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fmenu_item_cropped%2Fpublic%2Fmenu%2FGrilled-Mahi-Burrito_0.jpg%3Fitok%3D3KPkkW_9&h=aad04791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nburrito就係tortilla包住好撚多餡，正宗既會包飯係入面所以係好飽的，一條夠晒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://az616578.vo.msecnd.net/files/2016/07/18/636044104859117199985990752_tacos.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Faz616578.vo.msecnd.net%2Ffiles%2F2016%2F07%2F18%2F636044104859117199985990752_tacos.jpg&h=8354f224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTaco就咁對摺，食個陣好易跌晒出黎，個tortilla可脆可軟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://7b30cfc4a1b0ada1cdb2-893624c4eafa7bb58a8641a0ccf4ceea.ssl.cf1.rackcdn.com/chicken-sausage-quesadilla_thumb-m.jpg?mod=635703369177170000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F7b30cfc4a1b0ada1cdb2-893624c4eafa7bb58a8641a0ccf4ceea.ssl.cf1.rackcdn.com%2Fchicken-sausage-quesadilla_thumb-m.jpg%3Fmod%3D635703369177170000&h=a9dd9fff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nQuesadilla就係薄餅，兩塊tortilla上下夾住d餡，再好似pizza咁切黎食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/564x/e6/44/94/e64494622f1540bb5d4d41239357033e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2F564x%2Fe6%2F44%2F94%2Fe64494622f1540bb5d4d41239357033e.jpg&h=3e798721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外有個ranchero eggs ，tortilla上面有黑豆蓉芝士sour cream薯仔salsa青辣椒牛油果再有隻煎蛋，flying pan有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a978e97a6e5128ea62c73d0402765d1cea9a8a4c","tid":218792,"uid":58639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:19:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>trortilla, taaco, burrito 三者有咩唔同?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\ntortilla 好似只係個flatbread<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/28/031716_e76497bb9f05bbaa9e04f53598a52f1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F28%2F031716_e76497bb9f05bbaa9e04f53598a52f1f.jpg&h=92af2bfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ntaco 就係細細塊tortilla夾住啲料<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/28/031800_307a6997ddbcc65fc4b196fffe73f152.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F28%2F031800_307a6997ddbcc65fc4b196fffe73f152.jpg&h=ec20eb9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nburrito 就係大塊啲嘅tortilla包住啲料捲成成個wrap<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/28/031918_2579d080eb7f9d31d96934e1b3df0742.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F28%2F031918_2579d080eb7f9d31d96934e1b3df0742.jpg&h=1dacab4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9be5ac45dd18fb84c821635a31cc8324b8d8c769","tid":218792,"uid":58639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>trortilla, taaco, burrito 三者有咩唔同?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://images.wisegeek.com/flour-tortilla.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.wisegeek.com%2Fflour-tortilla.jpg&h=87d51f41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTortilla就係一塊塊圓形粟米餅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rubios.com/sites/default/files/styles/menu_item_cropped/public/menu/Grilled-Mahi-Burrito_0.jpg?itok=3KPkkW_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rubios.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fmenu_item_cropped%2Fpublic%2Fmenu%2FGrilled-Mahi-Burrito_0.jpg%3Fitok%3D3KPkkW_9&h=aad04791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nburrito就係tortilla包住好撚多餡，正宗既會包飯係入面所以係好飽的，一條夠晒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://az616578.vo.msecnd.net/files/2016/07/18/636044104859117199985990752_tacos.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Faz616578.vo.msecnd.net%2Ffiles%2F2016%2F07%2F18%2F636044104859117199985990752_tacos.jpg&h=8354f224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTaco就咁對摺，食個陣好易跌晒出黎，個tortilla可脆可軟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://7b30cfc4a1b0ada1cdb2-893624c4eafa7bb58a8641a0ccf4ceea.ssl.cf1.rackcdn.com/chicken-sausage-quesadilla_thumb-m.jpg?mod=635703369177170000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F7b30cfc4a1b0ada1cdb2-893624c4eafa7bb58a8641a0ccf4ceea.ssl.cf1.rackcdn.com%2Fchicken-sausage-quesadilla_thumb-m.jpg%3Fmod%3D635703369177170000&h=a9dd9fff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nQuesadilla就係薄餅，兩塊tortilla上下夾住d餡，再好似pizza咁切黎食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/564x/e6/44/94/e64494622f1540bb5d4d41239357033e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2F564x%2Fe6%2F44%2F94%2Fe64494