n<img src=\"http://az616578.vo.msecnd.net/files/2016/07/18/636044104859117199985990752_tacos.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Faz616578.vo.msecnd.net%2Ffiles%2F2016%2F07%2F18%2F636044104859117199985990752_tacos.jpg&h=8354f224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTaco就咁對摺，食個陣好易跌晒出黎，個tortilla可脆可軟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://7b30cfc4a1b0ada1cdb2-893624c4eafa7bb58a8641a0ccf4ceea.ssl.cf1.rackcdn.com/chicken-sausage-quesadilla_thumb-m.jpg?mod=635703369177170000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F7b30cfc4a1b0ada1cdb2-893624c4eafa7bb58a8641a0ccf4ceea.ssl.cf1.rackcdn.com%2Fchicken-sausage-quesadilla_thumb-m.jpg%3Fmod%3D635703369177170000&h=a9dd9fff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nQuesadilla就係薄餅，兩塊tortilla上下夾住d餡，再好似pizza咁切黎食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/564x/e6/44/94/e64494622f1540bb5d4d41239357033e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2F564x%2Fe6%2F44%2F94%2Fe64494622f1540bb5d4d41239357033e.jpg&h=3e798721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外有個ranchero eggs ，tortilla上面有黑豆蓉芝士sour cream薯仔salsa青辣椒牛油果再有隻煎蛋，flying pan有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩去左美國玩。去左chipotlet食，三者搞到亂晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實都係tortilla唔同包法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nChipotle<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> foodcourt之選"},{"pid":"50563c3eb09f6d3e5c88783d1278ac2b6751bf73","tid":218792,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:48:06.000Z","msg":"其實d餡係有唔同架，burrito有飯有豆有肉有芝士(最多)，taco(正宗唔係taco bell個種)就肉碎為主無芝士，quesadilla就芝士同肉粒<br />\n<br />\n至於係美國食到既墨西哥菜係Tex-mex美式墨西哥菜，其實已經係變奏左既，乜都加芝士牛油果一樣味<br />\n<br />\n其實連nachos甚至tortilla chips(doritos個種)都係美國野，墨西哥local餐廳係無得食架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，市中心遊客區先有，比d美國佬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4087e780bc60ce9cf25040e4de5595eec9d5e935","tid":218792,"uid":24519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:51:56.000Z","msg":"有無好食kebab<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201c09d1ef33510073f2224e0980faf601694975","tid":218792,"uid":34899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T21:50:36.000Z","msg":"歐洲周圍都有ge kebab doner 香港都係少之又少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cef6c218723b2616eae9d272fac6180a8491ccc","tid":218792,"uid":3120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T22:15:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港吊高晒嚟賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港幾時先有taco bell做爛市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTaco bell<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0356bbbf5d573889d7cd268e59707109ec0c3118","tid":218792,"uid":3120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T22:16:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無好食kebab<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尖沙咀有ge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75695f02f51235be0839c9647a40f492da43ddf","tid":218792,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T22:17:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歐洲周圍都有ge kebab doner 香港都係少之又少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食過幾歐kebab又大份又正，番到香港70幾蚊都唔好食，算吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a46a73d2fd68a796c65d14e32801359a60da8c","tid":218792,"uid":9146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T23:39:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實d餡係有唔同架，burrito有飯有豆有肉有芝士(最多)，taco(正宗唔係taco bell個種)就肉碎為主無芝士，quesadilla就芝士同肉粒<br />\n<br />\n至於係美國食到既墨西哥菜係Tex-mex美式墨西哥菜，其實已經係變奏左既，乜都加芝士牛油果一樣味<br />\n<br />\n其實連nachos甚至tortilla chips(doritos個種)都係美國野，墨西哥local餐廳係無得食架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，市中心遊客區先有，比d美國佬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nnachos + cheese sauce好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff72a0a197ce8b5e8c5a1f72c19807eac4a0821","tid":218792,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:36:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人試過cali mex</blockquote><br />\n食過佢既Quesadilla<br />\n唔錯, 半份都飽肚<br />\n不過唔平"},{"pid":"4ac8fa736343401dff4c345b328c5c1865750e97","tid":218792,"uid":52252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:42:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人試過cali mex</blockquote><br />\n正，成日食，周圍都有，又飽！burrito bowl都ok<br />\n咁當然無美國/墨西哥咁正啦....好想再去墨西哥食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTst tequila jack去過，無burrito的，taco tuesday就10蚊一個taco，但其實就好hea料唔算多，真係當小食送下酒就算，想食幾個填飽個肚就不如去calimex食個好味既taco/burrito<br />\n反而nacho就必食，buffalo wings都ok(其實nacho又好難唔好食既....)<br />\n<br />\nTaco bell之外我都想要in &amp; out呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我lunch去有burrito食，幾好食仲有碟幾大嘅沙律"},{"pid":"4b16b62cdd99b73b622c988491ebfc67d09de5b4","tid":218792,"uid":100423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:04:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西環 Tequila on Davis</blockquote><br />\n呢間高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26dcbae8be369d595e373d9d835e0c368d5e26b1","tid":218792,"uid":3602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T06:09:37.000Z","msg":"有冇d平民d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  類似chipotle"},{"pid":"d67d430978033f671c127752bce9f63c64d22044","tid":218792,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T13:10:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3037bb7bf70d32b2678d83624db7b861e59c8741","tid":218792,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T17:14:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aae460e9b753c25ce673854ff07099172255064d","tid":218792,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T13:14:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3baff063a82d79a6799c83bf811e5cd1939ae906","tid":218792,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T15:13:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f63653d68fcb3546ade9862de460ff306d0ffad5","tid":218792,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:51:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f447e07305ca840ba3f69d2080756c49f5661fa","tid":218792,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T17:03:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd3f98fe19ef69c2093be0b4388f9b05cde90fef","tid":218792,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T17:31:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e39f6b0168d9fdf79bfe449a3c87e192f321585","tid":218792,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:41:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"757c1a2c4f2bc35ec07249afa0b3222b14ca9b9a","tid":218792,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T10:59:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e51e625d269d5c0879b4b7199aaca7f45a34607","tid":218792,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T13:07:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1f42e7f676c4cf75b4055c165ca4299053b748